# Atlas AI Roadmap

## Vision

Atlas AI transforms market evidence into business intelligence by continuously monitoring AI models, public information, and industry trends.

Rather than measuring rankings, Atlas explains:

- What changed
- Why it changed
- What it means
- What should be done next

---

